headline.main: What’s on TV Friday: ‘Fire at Sea’ and ‘Vice: Trans Youth’

lead_paragraph: Former Chelsea midfielder Dennis Wise has likened N'Golo Kante to club great Claude Makelele and said the 25-year-old's stellar performance is one of the reasons the London side appear to be cruising towards the Premier League title.
